  "title": "Driver (Night Shift)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Requirements </strong><br />• Must be able speak, read and write simple English<br />• Must be able to work long hours and weekend (O/T Payable)<br />• Must have Class 3 OR Class 4 driving license<br />• Preferably with forklift driving license, with 1 year lorry driving experience<br />• Preferably with some exposure in Marine Industry but not a MUST<br />• Familiar with collection/delivery to PSA, Penjuru Terminal, Jurong Port and Local shipyards<br />• Operate forklift for loading and unloading<br />• Follow instruction from Logistics Supervisor & ensure timely collection and delivery of cargoes<br />• Perform delivery duties courteously and professionally<br />• Physically fit, hardworking and responsible<br />• With spirit of team work<br />• Able to start work immediately or within short notice.<br /></p><p>Working Hours: 10pm - 7am (Weekdays)</p>",
